Georges Denola https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_Denola 0 Georges Samson Denola (French: [dənɔla]; 29 August 1865, Paris, France – 3 March 1944, Neuilly-sur-Seine, France) was a French filmmaker and actor. His most notable film is La Jeunesse de Rocambole, released in 1913. As an actor, Georges Denola has been seen in L'Hirondelle et la Mésange, released in 1920, and in La Fin du jour, released in 1939.
